OL,3,C'Infected blood victim compensation
OL,4,Cfulfils vow I made 10 years ago' ` Hunt
OL,6,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt has said a
OL,7,Fcompensation package of at least #10
OL,8,Fbillion for victims of the infected
OL,9,Fblood scandal will fulfil a promise he
OL,10,Fmade to a constituent who died after
OL,11,Fcontracting hepatitis C.
OL,13,FTens of thousands of people were
OL,14,Finfected with contaminated blood or
OL,15,Fblood products between the 1970s and
OL,16,Fearly 1990s.
OL,18,FThe scandal ` dubbed the worst
OL,19,Ftreatment disaster in the history of
OL,20,Fthe NHS ` has been the subject of the
OL,21,Fbiggest ever public inquiry in the UK.
