OL,3,C'Infected blood victim compensation
OL,4,Cfulfils vow I made 10 years ago' ` Hunt
OL,6,FAnnouncing a compensation package for
OL,7,Fvictims in an interview in The Sunday
OL,8,FTimes, Mr Hunt told of how he promised
OL,9,Fto "sort" a fair and full settlement
OL,10,Fduring a meeting with campaigner Mike
OL,11,FDorricott in 2014.
OL,13,FMr Dorricott was 46 at the time, and
OL,14,Fhad learned just weeks before meeting
OL,15,FMr Hunt that he had terminal liver
OL,16,Fcancer ` a disease linked to the
OL,17,Fhepatitis C he contracted as a
OL,18,Fteenager from contaminated Factor 8
OL,19,Fblood products.
