OL,3,C'Infected blood victim compensation
OL,4,Cfulfils vow I made 10 years ago' ` Hunt
OL,6,F"I imagine after that meeting that
OL,7,FMike thought that he'd been fobbed off
OL,8,Fby yet another politician giving him
OL,9,Fthe runaround," he said, adding: "But
OL,10,Fwhat Mike didn't know was that he
OL,11,Freally had made a huge impression on
OL,12,Fme."
OL,14,FMr Hunt said the money will be funded
OL,15,Fthrough Government borrowing, and that
OL,16,Fthe package could be unveiled as soon
OL,17,Fas Tuesday ` when the final report of
OL,18,Fthe inquiry is due to be published.
