OL,3,C'Infected blood victim compensation
OL,4,Cfulfils vow I made 10 years ago' ` Hunt
OL,6,FHe said the Government would look
OL,7,F"very sympathetically" on any request
OL,8,Ffrom the victims or families for a
OL,9,Fnational memorial.
OL,11,F"What we want to do after Monday is
OL,12,Fvery close engagement with all the
OL,13,Ffamilies who've been through such hell
OL,14,Fand understand from them what the next
OL,15,Fsteps need to be," he said.
OL,17,FMr Dorricott's widow, Ann, 57, told
OL,18,Fthe paper that the announcement
OL,19,F"brings me solace".
